en freemium (source : Rapport sur les r\u00e9sultats trimestriels de Spotify au 1er trimestre 2021). La plateforme Spotify Ads repr\u00e9sente alors un grand potentiel pour les annonceurs qui souhaitent faire de la publicit\u00e9 pour toucher une large audience. Cet article vous propose d\u2019approfondir le sujet de la publicit\u00e9 sur la plateforme Spotify Advertising en comprenant mieux ce que c\u2019est, l\u2019utilit\u00e9 de ce levier mais \u00e9galement comment s\u2019en servir.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"image-single-wrapper text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/spotify.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Spotify\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/spotify.png 1920w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/spotify-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/spotify-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/spotify-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article article-table-matiere&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" 